    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a psychoanalyst and embark on a gripping journey of psychological drama. A woman plagued by recurring nightmares seeks your help. You must delve into her subconscious, deciphering strange and haunting symbolism to uncover the hidden truths buried within and solve the mystery behind her dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Full-Motion Video: Experience a deeply realistic narrative brought to life by Hollywood veterans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch as each emotion and revelation unfolds through live action video.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive Storytelling: Your questions guide the narrative. Choose carefully to uncover the patient's secrets<br>and piece together their story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Question Construction: Craft your own questions by combining topics the patient mentions, allowing for a personalized and engaging therapeutic journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological Depth: Explore complex themes like trauma, memory, and self-discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging Gameplay: Piece together clues from the patient's responses and use your psychoanalytical skills to interpret the symbolism in her dreams.</p>",
